Heads up for locals; there is a piton rock in the<br/>
second ledge in 'snakepit' (just below<br/>
Fishbowl) and the right exit rock is now<br/>
undercut since 2004 hurricanes. Consider<br/>
scouting. Tree below Surrealistic sneak. And<br/>
a left slot between Big Bang and Revelations<br/>
has a nasty pin rock in it now - drive left or run<br/>
the center ramp instead. &lt;br /&gt;<br/>
CW </div>
