Bear 20'' 4PM - usual suspects (brad, todd, mark, brent, lane, bryce) doing laps. New<br/>
<br/>
Forum: BoaterTalk<br/>
Date: Dec 08 2004, 8:25 GMT<br/>
From: ClayW<br/>
<br/>
Finally made it down and it was every bit as good as remembered.<br/>
There's 'new' wood in the surrealistic sneak (runnable?) and an 'new' undercut on the right in the<br/>
rapid below Fishbowl (Snakepit) and above Knockin on Heaven's Door. Meltdowns in Cosmic Trigger,<br/>
Corey ran left at Big Bang, then surfed Revelations (on my directions). Logs in left channel at<br/>
Armagaddon (still) but squeeky clean down from there.<br/>
65 degrees - in December? Love this season!<br/>
Clay<br/>
